name: RequestOfPhysician
title: Request of physician
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values represents a request made by a physician for an action such as administration of a medication, a laboratory test, or an intervention.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to give context to a Quality Data Model element, such as Medication, Administration or Intervention, Ordered.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to an attribute.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use the codes which represent the request of the physician.  Codes used are to be SNOMED-CT codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
